window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Beatrice isn’t the greatest witch in her village, but after her dearest friend suddenly dies, she will do anything to make certain his soul isn’t trapped in the ghost realm where the Headless Horseman resides.</p> <p>When Beatrice’s worst fear is realized, she vows to save Heath, even if it means becoming a ghost herself.</p> <p>Charmed by a Spell is a bite-sized paranormal historical romance novelette that is perfect for fans of friends to lovers and Bridgerton meets the Legend of Sleepy Hollow. This story is set in the same world as Bewitched by the Headless Horseman.</p>"; 
